## Do's and Don'ts

✅ **Do**:
- Write tests for new features
- Use type hints everywhere
- Follow existing patterns
- Run pre-commit before committing

❌ **Don't**:
- Put business logic in routes
- Skip validation with Pydantic
- Commit without running tests
- Ignore type errors
